  "paragraphs": [
    "Product only. Pricing exclusions apply. Contact a dealer for more information.",
    "Create a getaway outside your door. With stainless-steel construction, the Vesper ventless outdoor gas fireplace handles the elements. Place it anywhere with no venting or chimney needed. Get a big view of the flames with a 27\" tall opening either 36\" or 42\" wide. Pick from three real-life log sets accented by a traditional or herringbone brick interior.",
    "Add a finishing touch to enhance your fireplace and distinguish your home. Browse fireplace fronts that frame your opening and glass or mesh doors in colors to complement your décor. Colors on screen can vary. Connect with your local dealer online or in person to see actual samples.",
    "Add a finishing touch to enhance your fireplace and distinguish your home. Browse fireplace fronts that frame your opening and glass or mesh doors in colors to complement your décor. Colors on screen can vary. Connect with your local dealer online or in person to see actual samples.",
